<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="PN365-intro">
      <p type="edition">tiṇaiyum tuṟaiyum avai. mārkkaṇṭēyaṉār.
      </p>
      <p xml:lang="en" type="translation">  
      </p>
    </div>
    <div xml:id="PN365">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>mayaṅkiruṅ karuviya vicumpumuka ṉāka</l>
<l>viyaṅkiya virucuṭar kaṇṇeṉap peyariya</l>
<l>vaḷiyiṭai vaḻaṅkā vaḻakkaru nīttam</l>
<l>vayirak kuṟaṭṭiṉ vayaṅkumaṇi yārattup</l>
<l>poṉṉan tikiri muṉcamat turuṭṭip</l>
<l>porunark kāṇāc cerumiku muṉpiṉ</l>
<l>muṉṉōr cellavuñ cellā tiṉṉum</l>
<l>vilainalap peṇṭiriṉ palarmīk kūṟa</l>
<l>vuḷḷēṉ vāḻiyar yāṉeṉap paṉmā</l>
<l>ṇilamaka ḷaḻuta kāñciyu</l>
<l>muṇṭeṉa vuraipparā luṇarntici ṉōrē.</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>While, </l>
<l corresp="1">with the sky as a face that has masses of obscure dark [clouds], </l>
<l corresp="2">while the two stirring luminaries are named as eyes, </l>
<l corresp="3">in the flood difficult to navigate when the wind does not roam in between, </l>
<l corresp="4">with a string of glowing gems with a diamond frontlet </l>
<l corresp="5">rolling to the front battle on golden wheels, </l>
<l corresp="6">which much strength in fight which is not seen by fighters, </l>
<l corresp="7">not going even now, although those before did go, </l>
<l corresp="8">while many praise, like women whose beauty has a price, </l>
<l corresp="9">saying many times “I exist – let them live”, </l>
<l corresp="10">the lady earth cries, also transience exists, </l>
<l corresp="11">so say those indeed who have understood [the world]. </l>
</lg>
    </div>
